{"tid":1308041,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[此風不可長] 連登仔為咗割席可以去到幾盡？","createTime":"2019-07-11T19:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T04:13:20.000Z","uid":236704,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fc4eed257ec0b6876143e61451e368e7a1c3e1b7","tid":1308041,"uid":236704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:17:45.000Z","msg":"依家俾人打到趴在地，唔還手，咁都可以叫勇武，仲可以有幾千個正評。班真勇武派就咁俾班為左唔割和理非嘅人割走左。<br />\n<br />\n（技術分析） 琴晚嗰位手足根本係勇武到仆街<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306131\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306131</a><br />\n<br />\n你班撚樣為左爭光環可以顛到是非，同支那打飛機片有咩分別？輸都可以講到變贏。而且根本就冇赢到民意，對家當你做沙包，你又可以企定定俾人打，根本就係話俾班藍絲知我地剩係識扮慘搏同情，任打唔嬲，只會令班暴徒更加猖狂。藍黃中間嘅只會當你on9，俾人打到咁都唔還手，仲話俾人打唔應該還手，佢地點會幫你？<br />\n<br />\n我重申一次：打人唔啱，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔還手更加唔啱！</span>"},{"pid":"549649baf009b3b369260920f018f882d141c132","tid":1308041,"uid":236704,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:18:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f0943530165014a3b889c7dfbcbd4034d754245","tid":1308041,"uid":236704,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:20:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2945abbef0ba52f115a28f004e08dbceaae4c9","tid":1308041,"uid":156130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:20:39.000Z","msg":"(文宣幫忙)拉廢老反林鄭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1307966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1307966</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7dd4c6be069472e17a470b151011da7d529317c0","tid":1308041,"uid":236704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:22:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"227123a598b5f448d6d614c2df34c200a13e21f5","tid":1308041,"uid":236704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:23:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f3304be891dfdf736b8e3c5e8f8dbbf10008c7d","tid":1308041,"uid":40287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:33:46.000Z","msg":"暴力藍屍們見到打得咁happy， 唔識還手咁過癮，大大增加佢哋嘅信心，特別係廢叔廢伯，佢哋命唔長，所以特別放，有需要放棄連儂牆，因為藍屍有特權，加上好多超級聖人存在，只會搞到大家都攰，影響其他分支及主線。"},{"pid":"c145ab2d103247ccc2164f5458ed3e0456f4e278","tid":1308041,"uid":236704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:32:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aeaca7aa9eab89eacb1c9427bd4f886c093f1361","tid":1308041,"uid":236704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:19:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c115e62834fa312de372778214aa372f6a6fe43","tid":1308041,"uid":236704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:13:20.000Z","msg":"推"}]}